ttp://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_at_the_1952_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Japanese gymnasts\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_at_the_1952_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_at_the_1952_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Olympics\", \"from\": 494, \"to\": 512}, {\"ngram\": \"0.103 points\", \"from\": 535, \"to\": 547}, {\"ngram\": \"a sliver\", \"from\": 552, \"to\": 560}, {\"ngram\": \"a number\", \"from\": 564, \"to\": 572}, {\"ngram\": \"the minds\", \"from\": 597, \"to\": 606}, {\"ngram\": \"their head coach\", \"from\": 642, \"to\": 658}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 685, \"to\": 694}, {\"ngram\": \"those painful memories\", \"from\": 712, \"to\": 734}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We had the bitter experience of losing by the narrowest of margins, by 0.103,\\\" all-around titleholder Daiki Hashimoto told Reuters after a team training session in Tokyo last week.\", \"from\": 737, \"to\": 918, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 840, \"end\": 855, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daiki_Hashimoto\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Daiki Hashimoto\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daiki_Hashimoto\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daiki_Hashimoto\"}, {\"begin\": 861, \"end\": 868, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"score\": 0.9999999683709581, \"rank\": 3.162887275192046e-08, \"text\": \"Reuters\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\"}, {\"begin\": 902, \"end\": 907, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4937983910032014e-18, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the bitter experience\", \"from\": 745, \"to\": 766}, {\"ngram\": \"margins\", \"from\": 797, \"to\": 804}, {\"ngram\": \"a team training session\", \"from\": 875, \"to\": 898}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I want us to win that gold and enjoy the view from the podium.\\\"\", \"from\": 919, \"to\": 983, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 927, \"to\": 929}, {\"ngram\": \"that gold\", \"from\": 937, \"to\": 946}, {\"ngram\": \"the view\", \"from\": 957, \"to\": 965}, {\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 971, \"to\": 981}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"After losing to Russia by 0.103 in Tokyo, we have been working hard towards Paris fueled by a sense of revenge, so there is a part of me that's a bit sad that they will not be there,\\\" said Japan head coach Hisashi Mizutori, a former team gold medalist.\", \"from\": 985, \"to\": 1238, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1002, \"end\": 1008, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9679922930235372, \"rank\": 0.03299959483863384, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1021, \"end\": 1026, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4937983910032014e-18, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 1062, \"end\": 1067, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999167812, \"rank\": 8.321650772081032e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1175, \"end\": 1180, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990